computer said that she has a maximal signature... well If she like it 
or not she's now loyal to Predacon's cause... and why are maximals 
now interested to rescue an insignificant Scout while a good warrior 
had been captured???? If Maximal said that they are loyals each other 
why they don't act according to their words? "
